# Task Tracker API

This is a simple backend project built using **Node.js**, **Express**, and **MongoDB**.
The purpose of this project is to create a basic task management system where users can add, view, update, and delete tasks.

I created this project to practice backend development concepts such as **REST APIs, routing, middleware, and database integration**. It helps to understand how a backend server handles requests and stores data in a database.

## Features

* Create a new task
* View all tasks
* Update task status
* Delete tasks

## Technologies Used

* Node.js
* Express.js
* MongoDB
* Mongoose

## Purpose

This project is mainly built for learning and improving backend development skills.
